SmallWorld Search Engine

= Build (commandline and Eclipse) =
Ensure the following:-

* environment variable JAVA_HOME is correctly set
  export JAVA_HOME=<path to jdk installation>
* environment variable CATALINA_HOME is correctly set
  export CATALINA_HOME=<path to tomcat installation>
* for eclipse ant builder setup, ensure the following:-
** under <project> --(right-click)--> Properties --> Builders --> New/Edit... --> Ant Builder --> JRE --> Execution environment: --> select appropriate environment
** under <project> --(right-click)--> Properties --> Builders --> New/Edit... --> Ant Builder --> Environment --> New --> set CATALINA_HOME=<path to tomcat installation>
 
